31.336Z","comments_closed?":false,"facebook_team?":false,"team_private?":false,"vulnerability_information":"###Vulnerability:\nPassword Reset Link not expiring after changing the email\n\n###Proof Of Concept:\n\n1.Send the password reset link to your email.\n2.Don`t open the password link just copy it and paste into any editor.\n3.Open your account.\n4.Go to your account settings.\n5.Under account, you will see Account Overview.\n6.Go to the Email and password Option and change the email and verify it.\n7.After changing the email go to your password reset link which you copied.\n8.Change your password.\n\n\nBooM password Changed.\n\n#####Thanks\n\n## Impact\n\nThe attacker can still change the password if victim thinks his/her account is compromised and decided to change his/her email.","vulnerability_information_html":"\u003ch3 id=\"vulnerability\"\u003eVulnerability:\u003c/h3\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003ePassword Reset Link not expiring after changing the email\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch3 id=\"proof-of-concept\"\u003eProof Of Concept:\u003c/h3\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e1.Send the password reset link to your email.\u003cbr\u003e\n2.Don`t open the password link just copy it and paste into any editor.\u003cbr\u003e\n3.Open your account.\u003cbr\u003e\n4.Go to your account settings.\u003cbr\u003e\n5.Under account, you will see Account Overview.\u003cbr\u003e\n6.Go to the Email and password Option and change the email and verify it.\u003cbr\u003e\n7.After changing the email go to your password reset link which you copied.\u003cbr\u003e\n8.Change your password.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eBooM password Changed.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch5 id=\"thanks\"\u003eThanks\u003c/h5\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"impact\"\u003eImpact\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe attacker can still change the password if victim thinks his/her account is compromised and decided to change his/her email.\u003c/p\u003e\n","bounty_amount":"100.0","formatted_bounty":"$100","weakness":{"id":27,"name":"Improper Authenti